{"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "247818559716598", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12522311_247584632370558_6354352381550919680_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KK7PpRFKrD8Q7kNvgH1u8jR&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AHZa2OD0lLxpB7BLDU6Tsw-&oh=00_AYC4IhSQgVNLZ5eFVZqihXSfSBH8zUyUJ0DP6cj5DIblKQ&oe=66F16373"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "668476670569937", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12482153_1858067167798991_7217008734889836544_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=fLSgjLpRu5YQ7kNvgGQoUsx&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AHZa2OD0lLxpB7BLDU6Tsw-&oh=00_AYAeB5mANRh8DizMDgapth6cz2FQQwffT9qbsnSk14VYAQ&oe=66F15D71"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "FlowForBreathVR", "keywords": ["Relax", "Meditation", "Calm", "Flow"], "long_description": "Flow for Breath VR is a mobile VR app that will help center your thoughts and calm your mind through deep breathing exercises. \n\nDeep breathing is a natural tranquilizer and, practiced in an all immersive environment, it has far reaching benefits. The practice of deep breathing has the following benefits:\n\n1. increases serotonin and calms the mind\n2. helps expel damaging toxins\n3. lowers heart and respiratory rates\n4. lowers blood pressure\n5. enhances mood\n\nChoose any one of five state settings:\n1. Happiness\n2. Calm\n3. Focus\n4. Energize\n5. Core breathing\n\nIt was researched and created by a clinical hypnotherapist and mindfulness coach to bring you a quick and efficient method to shift into a state of balance, flow, health and focus with ease.\n\nChoose your path and be on your way to deeper breathing effortlessly. Like sitting in a hot tub with mineral spring water and soaking in whole body wellness inside and out.", "short_description": "Flow for Breath VR will help center your thoughts and calm your mind."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://